      <td><b>World Value Models</b> (Wang et al., 2026)</td>
      <td>Repurposes a pretrained video world model as a generalist value estimator, using a Mixture-of-Transformers to keep value tokens from interfering with generation.</td>
      <td>Value models are the natural filter for mixed-quality data, but VLMs have weak temporal priors. World models do not, and the new Suboptimal-Value-Bench tests hesitation and retry modes.</td>
