      <td>GRPO post-training that extends reliable action-chunk length and prunes redundant physical steps.</td>
      <td>Even good VLAs waste inference calls on tail-degraded chunks and corrective wiggles. PolicyTrim reports 3× chunk utilization, 51.4% fewer steps, and up to 5.83× end-to-end speedup.</td>
